data.description: PRICED TO SELL!!!!  Welcome HOME! This exceptional home represents the original model of the community, making it the crown jewel of the neighborhood. Prepare to be dazzled as you step into this newer and modern house, meticulously designed with every imaginable upgrade, bell, and whistle.  With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a loft, this home offers an abundance of space for both relaxation and entertainment. From the moment you enter, you'll be greeted by impeccable craftsmanship and high-end finishes that exude sophistication and style. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow throughout the house, providing a perfect setting for creating lifelong memories.  As you explore further, you'll discover a fully fenced backyard, offering a serene and private retreat. Imagine spending tranquil evenings or hosting gatherings in this beautifully landscaped outdoor oasis. Whether it's enjoying a morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends and family, this backyard is the ideal space to unwind and enjoy the outdoors.  Located in close proximity to the renowned Disney parks, this home offers the convenience of easy access to endless entertainment options. Experience the magic of Disney at your doorstep, creating cherished memories for years to come. Additionally, you'll find yourself surrounded by an array of exceptional restaurants, shops, and amenities, ensuring that every need and desire is met with ease.  What sets this property apart even further is its very low HOA fees. Experience the benefits of a well-maintained community without compromising your budget. This feature enhances the overall value of this home, making it an incredibly enticing opportunity.    Don't miss the chance to own the original model home, the epitome of luxury living. Indulge in the upgrades, relish the bells and whistles, and bask in the comfort and prestige of this remarkable residence. Make this extraordinary house your forever home and enjoy a lifestyle of unparalleled refinement.
